<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>فِي مَجْلِسِ الأَمْنِ الظَّلُومْ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>* * *<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>أَنَا مَا رَأَيْتُ الْيَوْمَ أَرْخَصَ مِنْ دِمَائِكْ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>دُنْيَاكَ تَشْهَدُ أَرْضُهَا<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>وَالنَّجْمُ يَشْهَدُ فِي سَمَائِكْ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>وَالْكَوْنُ يَبْكِي حِينَ يَذْكُرُ مِنْ إِبَائِكْ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>مُنْذُ الْقُرُونِ الْغَابِرَةْ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>أَنَسِيتَ يَوْمًا قَدْ أَتَى الإِسْلامُ فِيهْ<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>لِيُعِزَّ قَوْمًا أَنْتُمُ لَهُمُ الشَّبِيهْ<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>كَانُوا شَرَاذِمَ مِثْلَكُمْ<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>وَهَوَانُهُمْ بَيْنَ الأُمَمْ<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>كَهَوَانِكُمْ<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>فَأَتَاهُمُ الإِسْلامُ عِزًّا فِي الْحَيَاةِ<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>